import React from 'react'
import { Container, Input, InputConatiner, LogoImg, Menu, MenuRight, Row, Wrapper } from './styles'
import Button from '../button'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <Wrapper>
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <LogoImg src='./logo.webp' alt='logo'/>
                <InputConatiner>
                    <Input placeholder="buscar..."/>
                </InputConatiner>
                <Menu>live code</Menu>
                <Menu>Global</Menu>
            </Row>
            <Row>
                <MenuRight>
                    <Button title="Home" variant="primary"/>
                    <Button title="Entrar"/>
                    <Button title="Cadastrar-se"/>
                </MenuRight>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    </Wrapper>
  )
}

export {Header}
